  "title": "Sales Manager (Audio Visual)",
  "description": "<p>Our esteemed client in the <strong>ICT industry</strong> is seeking a <strong>Sales Manager </strong>to join their dynamic team:</p><ul><li><strong>Employment Type: </strong>Permanent</li><li><strong>Position:</strong> Sales Manager (Public Sector/ Regional Markets)</li><li><strong>Location:</strong> West</li><li><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Monday to Friday, office hours</li><li><strong>Salary Package:</strong> Up to $5,000 + Commission + Transport Allowance + Bonus</li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Design and execute sales strategies to expand market share in government/public sector or multi-region markets.</li><li>Identify, prospect, and nurture relationships with institutional and corporate clients.</li><li>Lead negotiations, presentations, and product demonstrations for complex technology solutions.</li><li>Analyze market trends, competitor activity, and client requirements to refine sales approaches.</li><li>Partner with engineering, product, and marketing teams to align solutions with client needs.</li><li>Manage sales pipelines, forecasts, and performance reports for senior leadership.</li><li>Oversee budget allocation for regional/government sales operations, ensuring cost efficiency.</li><li>Research emerging technologies and untapped market opportunities.</li><li>Ensure post-sale client satisfaction through follow-ups and proactive support.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>At least NITEC with minimum 2 years of sales experience within ICT, AV, or enterprise software industry, preferably with exposure to public sector/ government agencies.</li><li>Willing to travel as and when needed.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Ready to apply? Here’s how:</strong></p><ul><li>Click the APPLY button, or</li><li>Email your resume (in MS Word or PDF format) to <a href=\"mailto:adelin@intuitrecruitment.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>adelin@intuitrecruitment.com</strong>.</a> Include the job title in your email subject line for prompt processing.</li></ul><p><em><strong>Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></em></p><p><br /></p><p>By submitting your application, you consent to the collection and use of your personal data under Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p><br /></p><p>Adelin Chong | EA Personnel Reg No.: R1875641</p><p>Intuit Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 25C2793</p>",
